        "Excellent quality and fast shipping! Our customers love the eco-friendly packaging,
        and it's helped strengthen our brand identity."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="text-xl font-semibold">Sarah M.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral/60">Restaurant Owner</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
